titles.title: Lead Me To The Rock That Is Higher Than I

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
Lead me to the Rock that is higher than I,
For You have been my refuge, and I can trust in You.
Unfailing fortress in the midst of all my battles,
Lead me to the Rock that is higher than I.

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
Llévame a la roca más alta que yo
Tú has sido mi refugio y en ti confío yo
Torre fuerte has sido delante del enemigo
Llévame a la roca más alta que yo.
